Package review.classdesign.jammy.addons

Addon API that should be implemented in order to add language support.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILanguageManager
    An ILanguageManager is in charge of managing problem solver execution by providing for a given problem, following features : Retrieving a valid project instance Retrieving a valid solver file Run a given solver file for a given output.
    ISolverRunner
    An ISolverRunner represents a solver execution for a given input.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractProcessManager
    Abstract ILanguageManager implementation tat aims to run solver through Process instance.
    DatasetBuilder
    A DatasetBuilder provides tools for extracting and creating sample dataset for a given Problem instance.
    ProcessSolverRunner
    ISolverRunner implementation used for language that are ran through a Process.

Package review.classdesign.jammy.addons Description
